data.description:
Welcome to 7518 Rome Oriskany Road, a unique beautiful welcoming at first sight. This home features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths and 1 half bath. Primary bedroom with full bath, and a beautiful balcony to enjoy the sunrises and sunsets. Freshly painted inside and outside - 2023. The owner has made numerous upgrades: Seamless gutter - 2022; Retaining wall - 2022; new sidewalk - Aug 2023; Attic - Fully insulated by Standard insulation - 2022; New window and sliding glass door overlooking the private backyard - 2022. Living room with fireplace.
This home features an additional family room with an additional 734 square feet, gas fireplace,  fourth bedroom, lower level laundry room; half bath; exterior walk out and two stall attached garage. 
When you ask for a home that is ready to move in, this is the home.
